WEBVTT

00:07.455 --> 00:09.921
Forward, march!

00:16.955 --> 00:19.888
Halt!
Make ready!

00:19.921 --> 00:22.288
Aim! Fire!

00:24.455 --> 00:27.389
Fire!

00:27.422 --> 00:29.322
Forward! March!

00:33.489 --> 00:34.855
Halt!

00:34.888 --> 00:36.422
Make ready!

00:36.455 --> 00:37.422
Aim!

00:37.455 --> 00:39.055
Fire!

00:42.888 --> 00:45.821
Forward! March!

00:45.855 --> 00:47.554
Halt!

00:47.588 --> 00:50.621
Aim! Fire!

00:52.088 --> 00:54.855
Making croissants
seems daunting,

00:54.888 --> 00:57.255
but really it's as easy
as making coq au vin.

00:57.288 --> 01:00.322
- To think it takes two days.
- Mm-hmm.

01:00.355 --> 01:01.588
Hey, Julia Childs, I could buy
a tube of those crescent things

01:01.621 --> 01:04.788
and serve 'em to you
in 20 minutes.

01:04.821 --> 01:06.455
No! Throw it to second!
Come on!

01:06.489 --> 01:08.455
W-why are you yelling?
You can't change the outcome.

01:08.489 --> 01:10.489
Really?

01:10.521 --> 01:12.288
Gee, I thought I could.

01:12.322 --> 01:14.389
That would require crossing
the space-time continuum.

01:14.422 --> 01:18.322
Go get the hand vacuum

01:18.355 --> 01:20.355
and clean up your couch crumbs.

01:20.389 --> 01:21.855
Ma, I'm trying to relax.

01:21.888 --> 01:24.554
Okay, and we are trying
to get ready for a guest.

01:24.588 --> 01:26.155
<i>Help out.</i>

01:30.022 --> 01:32.654
Come on, Maura, you're gonna
give yourself an ulcer.

01:32.688 --> 01:34.855
All right? It's not royalty.
It's your mom.

01:34.888 --> 01:37.688
Ulcers are caused by H. Pylori,
a bacteria.

01:37.721 --> 01:38.921
Or critical mothers.

01:38.955 --> 01:40.455
I'm not critical.

01:40.489 --> 01:41.755
Am I?

01:41.788 --> 01:43.422
She's never been
to my house before.

01:43.455 --> 01:45.322
Never?

01:45.355 --> 01:47.255
Well, what do you do
when she visits Boston?

01:47.288 --> 01:51.521
We just usually go to one
of my parents' homes in Europe.

01:52.355 --> 01:54.755
Those tulips are wilting
already.

01:54.788 --> 01:57.489
Yes, I could see
why you're so ashamed

01:57.521 --> 01:58.955
of this hideous place,

01:58.988 --> 02:02.855
<i>and forcing her to stay
in that disgusting guesthouse.</i>

02:02.888 --> 02:05.888
- What are you talking about?
- It's lovely. - Wait a minute.

02:05.921 --> 02:07.955
<i>If your mom is in the
guesthouse, where are you staying?</i>

02:07.988 --> 02:09.955
With you, of course.

02:09.988 --> 02:13.755
Fine, but just know
I don't serve coq au vin.

02:13.788 --> 02:16.521
I serve...Cocoa puffs.

02:16.554 --> 02:17.855
I know.

02:19.588 --> 02:22.521
Rizzoli.
Isles.

02:22.554 --> 02:25.055
- Okay. I'll be right there. 
- I'm on my way.

02:26.721 --> 02:28.688
I haven't even had a chance
to pre-order

02:28.721 --> 02:30.389
the organic pig's trotters.

02:30.422 --> 02:32.521
Are those feet?
I'm not eating feet.

02:32.554 --> 02:34.422
- I'm gonna leave you the butcher's number.
- Sure.

02:35.022 --> 02:37.055
Come on.

02:37.088 --> 02:38.688
You should change.

02:38.721 --> 02:40.355
All right.
I'll change in the car.

02:40.389 --> 02:41.721
<i>Then I'm driving.</i>

02:41.755 --> 02:43.721
Oh, come on.
I hate it when you drive.

02:43.755 --> 02:46.022
Well, I hate it more
when you undress and drive.

02:46.055 --> 02:47.888
Bye, ma.

